snippet.title: Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka | Thamma | Nora F, Ayushmann K, Rashmika M |Sachin-Jigar, Rashmeet K, Amitabh B
snippet.description:
Presenting "Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka" from "Thamma". Feat. Nora Fatehi, Ayushmann Khurrana and Rashmika Mandanna.

Song Credits 
Featuring: Nora Fatehi, Ayushmann Khurrana and Rashmika Mandanna
Music : Sachin-Jigar 
Singer : Rashmeet Kaur, Jigar Saraiya
Lyrics : Amitabh Bhattacharya 
Programmed & Arranged : Sachin- Jigar, Abhishek Singh, Hrishikesh Gangan, Amrit Sharma @ White Noise Collectives
Backing Vocals : Abhishek Singh, Amrit Sharma
Music Production Head : Romil Ved
Acoustic, Electric Guitars ,Bass & Strokes : Rhythm Shaw
Recording Engineer : Susmeet Rewaskar @ White Noise Collectives
Mixed & Mastered : Eric Pillai @ FSOB
Assistant Mixing Engineer : Michael Edwin Pillai
Music Label : T-Series

Maddock Films presents "Thamma"
In Cinemas on 21st October.

#NoraFatehi #Dilbar #Thamma

Cast: Ayushmann Khurrana, Rashmika Mandanna, Paresh Rawal, Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Faisal Malik, Rachit Singh
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan, Amar Kaushik
Directed By: Aditya Sarpotdar
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota, Pooja Prem Patheja
Director of Photography: Saurabh Goswami (ISC)
Music / Background Score: Sachin‚ÄìJigar
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya
Costume Designer: Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
Director of Choreography: Vijay A. Ganguly
Publicity Design: Himanshu & Rahul Nanda (H-One)

Lyrics:

Haan, Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyar Na Kiya
Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyar Na Kiya

Na Kiya
Na Kiya, Jisne Pyar Na Kiya
Kya Kiya, Kya Kiya
Kya Kiya, Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Aankhon Ko Aankhon Se Kisi Ki Chaar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Pyaar Saccha Agar Chahiye
Toh Dua Mein Asar Chahiye
Pyaar Saccha Agar Chahiye
Toh Dua Mein Asar Chahiye
Buzdilon Ka Nahi Kaam Yeh
Pyaar Mein Toh Jigar Chahiye

Ishq Hua Par Khulke Izhaar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya
Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Na Kiya
Na Kiya, Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya
Kya Kiya, Kya Kiya
Kya Kiya, Jisne Pyar Na Kiya

snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Survival Stage | Day 1
snippet.description:
The final chance to reach the Grand Finals is here. The 16 remaining teams from the Semi Finals who fell short of the Top 8 now face off in an intense BGMI survival battle. Every match counts and every fight could end their journey. Only the Top 8 teams will move forward to the Grand Finals.

Expect clutch plays, unpredictable zone shifts, and all-out chaos as these teams fight to stay alive and push the game Beyond Limits!

Teams Playing:
Madkings
Blitz Esports
Phoenix Esports
Vasista Esports
iQOO8BIT
OnePlus Cincinnati Kids
Autobotz Esports
mysterious4 Esports
GENESIS ESPORTS 
FS ESPORTS
Likitha Esports
Victores Sumus
Nebula Esports
META NINZA
myG Los Hermanos
First Curiosity

Map Rotation:
Match 1: Erangel
Match 2: Miramar
Match 3: Sanhok
Match 4: Sanhok
Match 5: Miramar
Match 6: Erangel

Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh‚Äôs music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. snippet.title: Patriot Malayalam Teaser | Mammootty | Mohanlal | Mahesh Narayanan | Anto Joseph
snippet.description:
From Anto Joseph Productions, the banner behind some of the most acclaimed and celebrated films in recent times, and visionary filmmaker Mahesh Narayanan comes the Official Teaser of Patriot.

Featuring an ensemble of legends: Mammootty, Mohanlal, Fahadh Faasil, Kunchacko Boban, Nayanthara, and Revathy.

Watch Hindi Teaser: https://youtu.be/j3iXh5ipGmw
Watch Telugu Teaser: https://youtu.be/kzGyAfEJWt0
Watch Tamil Teaser: https://youtu.be/WfGTzc4TsU4

Written & Directed by : Mahesh Narayanan 
Produced by:  Anto Joseph, K G Anil Kumar
Co Produced by : C R Saleem, Subhash George Manuel
Music & Original Score  : Sushin Shyam 
Teaser music mixed- Abin paul
Director of Photography : Manush Nandan ISC
Executive producers: C V Sarathi, Rajesh krishna
Editing : Mahesh Narayanan, Rahul Radhakrishnan
Production Design : Shajie Naduvil, Jibin Jacob
Audiography: Vishnu Govind
Sync Sound : Vaisakh P 
Production Controller: Dixon Poduthas
Line Producers : Sunil Singh, Niroop Pinto, Justin Boban, Jeswin Boban
Make Up: Ranjith Ambady
Lyrics : Anwar Ali
Stunts : Dhilip Subbarayan
Stunt Silva, Mafia Sasi, Riyas- Habib
Costume Design: Dhanya Balakrishanan
Choreography: Shobi Paulraj 
Vfx:Firefly , Eggwhite , Identvfxlab
Chief Associate Director: Linu Antony
Associate Director: Phantom Praveen
Di Colorist : Ashirwad Hadkar ISC
Titles : Sarathvinu
Subtitles : Vivek Renjit (Break Borders)
Stills: Navin Murali
Publicity Design:Aesthetic Kunjamma
PRO : Vaisakh C Vadakkeveedu

snippet.title: Pariyan Vargi | Gulab Sidhu | Nirvair Pannu | Tanu Grewal | SVCW | 10 October | Jass Records
snippet.description:
‚ú®Pariyan Vargi is not just a song ‚Äî it‚Äôs a romantic vibe beautifully expressed in the soulful vocals of Gulab Sidhu. Penned and composed by Dharp, the track tells the story of a boy who imagines a girl as a fairy in his dreams, wondering how she would look if he ever met her in reality. In a poetic way, he says that when she looks into the mirror, even the mirrors would lose themselves in her beauty.

üé¨ ‚ÄúSoohe Ve Cheere Waleya‚Äù 

üåé Worldwide Releasing on 10th Oct 2025

localized.description:
‚ú®Pariyan Vargi is not just a song ‚Äî it‚Äôs a romantic vibe beautifully expressed in the soulful vocals of Gulab Sidhu. Penned and composed by Dharp, the track tells the story of a boy who imagines a girl as a fairy in his dreams, wondering how she would look if he ever met her in reality. In a poetic way, he says that when she looks into the mirror, even the mirrors would lose themselves in her beauty.

snippet.title: Kaka - Heer (Official Video) | Waris Shah | Punjabi Trandional Song 2025
snippet.description:
Kaka Ji Records Presents Kaka Ji New Song "Heer"

Singer - Kaka 
Music - kaka
Lyrics- waris shah
Video director -Robby Singh Padda 
Mix Master -Stereo Shinobi
Female lead -Kavya thakur 
Assistant director - Jagteshwar thind,Gurlal benipal
line Production- sukhi Khattra.
Costumes stylist- Khwaish mehta
Makeup- Manisha makeover
Produced by - Raghbir Singh,Gurpreet Singh , Gurwinder Tiwana 
Project by -Sahejpal Singh Sidhu

Enjoy And Stay Connected With Artist || Kaka
https://www.instagram.com/kaka._.ji?igsh=MTJ5d3lobHFzZDQwcg==
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoBZjU5zDSWhlewGr3KJdrg

Ranjha aakhda khiaal na pawo mere, sapp sheeh fakeer da des keha.
Koonjan waang mamuliyaan des chhade, asaan zaat sifat te bhes keha.
Watan damaan de naal te zaat jogi, sanu saak kabeelrha khesh keha.
Jehra watan te jat wal dhiaan rakhe, duniyaan daar hai oh darvesh keha.


Main ikallrha gall na jaan‚Äôna haan, tusi dovein nanaan bharjaaiyan ni.
Malzadiyan waang banaa teri, payi baithi hain suram-salaaiyan ni.
Pair pakkarh fakeer de te de bhikhia, arhiyan kehiyan kawariye laiyan ni.
dhyann rab te rakh , na ho tatti, gusse hon na bhaliyan deeyaan jaaiyan ni.
Tainu shauk hai tinan da bhagparriye, jinnaan daachiyan bahar charaaiyan ni.
Waris Shah ohh sadaa hi jindde ne, jinnaan keetiyaan neik kamaaiyan ni.

Dil fikar ne gheriya band hoya, Ranjha jiu gotey lakh khai baitha.
Sathon hoonj dhuaan sir cha turia, kaale bagh vich dher machai baitha.
Akhiyan meet ke rab dhiaan dhar ke, chare taraf hai dhunrha laai baitha.
Waris Shah us waqt nu jhoorda ee, jis velrhe akhiyaan laai baitha.

Heer naike patt da pahin tewar, waali itar faleel malanwaudi hai.
Kanjal bhinne neinn apraadh lathe, dovey husan de kattak le dhaanwdi hai.
Ranjha vekh ke aakhda pari koi, ikke bhawein taan Heer siyaal hove.
Koi hoor ki mohni indraani, Heer hove taan saiyan de naal howe.
Waris Shah aayi chambrhi Ranjhane nu, jeha gadhe de gaale vich laal hoye.


Awull pairr pakkrhe itaqaak karke, fer naal kalejhe de lag gayi.
Nawan taor ajube da nazar aaya, vekho jal patang te agg gayi.
Kehi lag gayi chinaga jag gayi, khabar jag gayi vajj dharagh gayi.
Yaaro thaggan di rihuryi Heer jatti, muh lagadiyaan yaar nu thagg gayi.
Agge dhoonwaan dhukhendrha jogirhe da, utton phook ke jhugrhe agg gayi.
Yaar yaar da bagh vich mel hoya, gall aam mashhoor ho jag gayi.
Waris tarutiyan nu rabb melda ae, vekho kamle nu pari lag gayi.


Heer ho rukhsat Ranjhe yaar kolon, aakhe sahitiye mata pakaiye ni.
Mere waaste us ne lae tarale, kiven us di aas pujaiye ni.



Aggon raiba sairfaan boliyan ne, keha bhabiye ni matha kherhiya ee.
Nain shokh hoye rang chamak aaiya, koi jobne da khooh gediyaa ee.
Nain mast gallan teriyan laal hoyiyan, dukkan bhann choli vich teliyaan ni.
Kise hik teri naal hik jodi, pedu naal valoodran meliyan ni.
Teriyaan gallan te dandan de daarah disan, ajj sodhiyaan thakaran cheliyaan ni.
Ajj nahi iyaaliyan khabar ladhi, baghiyaarann ne roliyaan cheliyaan ni.


Parnehan da mainu asar hoya, rang jarad hoya ese waaste ni.
shhapan khubb gayiyan gallan meriyan te, daag laal peye ese waaste ni.
Katte jaande nu bhaj ke mili saan main, tainiyan dhilliyan ne ese waaste ni.
Runni athru dulle san mukhde te, khull gaye tatolrhey paasate ni.
Mudhi payi banere te vekhdi saan, pedu laal hoye ese waaste ni.
Surakhi hothaan di aape mai chuus layi, rang udd gaya ese waaste ni.
Katta ghuttiya vich galvakadi de, dukkan laal hoyiyan ese waaste ni.
Mere pedu nu katte ne thudd maari, laasaan bhakhlan diyan mere mass te ni.
Hor puchh waris main gharibni nu, ki aakhde lok muhasate ni.


#warisshahkalam #warisshah  #Heerwarisshah #tradionalsong #heertradionalsong kaka new song,kaka new song #HeerWarisShah #SufiLoveStory #PunjabiEpic #IshqHaqiqi #WarisShah #HeerRanjha #SufiPoetry #PunjabiCulture #ClassicLiterature #IslamicRomance #SufiKalam #NewKalam, #PunjabiKalam #KalamBabaBulheShah
